---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import stairliftImg from '../assets/stairlift-curved.jpg';
---

<Layout 
  title="Stairlifts Rochester NY | Curved & Straight Stair Lifts Buffalo Syracuse"
  description="Professional stairlift installation for Rochester, Buffalo and Syracuse NY homes. Straight, curved and outdoor models with free in-home consultations."
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
    <nav class="text-sm mb-6 text-slate-500">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-slate-700">Home</a> <span class="mx-1">/</span> 
      <span class="text-slate-700">Stairlifts</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-10 items-start">
      <div>
        <span class="text-sky-600 font-semibold tracking-wider text-sm">ACCESS YOUR HOME AGAIN</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter mt-3 mb-6">Stairlifts</h1>

        <div class="prose prose-lg text-slate-700 max-w-prose">
          <p>
            A stairlift is one of the best solutions for navigating your staircase, helping you access parts of your home 
            that may have become difficult to reach. Blending seamlessly into your home with a smooth start and stop mechanism, 
            you can glide effortlessly up and down the stairs.
          </p>
          <p>
            Are you finding it challenging to navigate the steps inside or outside your home? Freedom Mobility NY offers 
            expert guidance and professional installation of high-quality stairlifts from leading manufacturers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-slate-900 text-white px-7 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold inline-flex items-center gap-2">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
          <a href="tel:5854880771" class="border px-7 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold inline-flex items-center">(585) 488-0771</a>
        </div>

        <ul class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span> Straight &amp; curved staircases</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span> Indoor and outdoor models</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span> Battery backup standard</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span> Folding rails for narrow stairs</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span> Swivel seats for safe transfer</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">✓</span> Heavy-duty weight capacities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 shadow">
        <Image src={stairliftImg} alt="Curved stairlift in a residential home" class="w-full" width="800" height="600" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        <div class="bg-white p-6 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Example of a curved stairlift installation. We handle complex staircases with precision.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- More info / brands -->
  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-t border-b py-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-semibold tracking-tight text-2xl mb-6">We install stairlifts from trusted manufacturers</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-10 gap-y-4 text-slate-600 text-sm">
        <a href="https://ameriglide.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">AmeriGlide</a>
        <a href="https://www.harmar.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Harmar</a>
        <a href="https://www.bruno.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Bruno</a>
        <a href="https://www.stannah.com/stairlifts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Stannah</a>
        <a href="https://www.acornstairlifts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Acorn</a>
        <a href="https://www.handicare.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Handicare</a>
        <span class="text-slate-400">+ many more</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm max-w-prose text-slate-600">During your free consultation we will recommend the best model for your staircase, budget, and lifestyle.</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm"><a href="/brands" class="text-sky-600 hover:underline font-medium">View all our trusted brands &amp; partners →</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <a href="/contact" class="block w-full sm:w-auto text-center sm:inline-block bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 transition text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl">Get your free stairlift consultation today →</a>
  </div>

  <!-- Internal Linking: Locations for this service -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Stairlifts Available in These Areas</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
      <a href="/locations/rochester/stairlifts" class="p-4 border rounded hover:bg-slate-50">Stairlifts in Rochester, NY →</a>
      <a href="/locations/buffalo/stairlifts" class="p-4 border rounded hover:bg-slate-50">Stairlifts in Buffalo, NY →</a>
      <a href="/locations/syracuse/stairlifts" class="p-4 border rounded hover:bg-slate-50">Stairlifts in Syracuse, NY →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">We also serve surrounding communities. <a href="/locations" class="underline">View all locations</a>.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ for Featured Snippets (Best-in-Class SEO) -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions About Stairlifts</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
        <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">How much does a stairlift cost in Rochester, Buffalo, or Syracuse?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Pricing varies based on the model (straight vs curved), length of the staircase, and any custom features. Most straight stairlifts start around $3,000–$5,000 installed. We provide free in-home quotes with no obligation.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
        <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">Can stairlifts be installed on curved stairs?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Yes. We specialize in custom curved stairlifts that fit the unique shape of your staircase in older Rochester, Buffalo, and Syracuse homes.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
        <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">How long does installation take?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Most straight stairlifts can be installed in a few hours. Curved models typically take 1–2 days. Our technicians are clean and respectful of your home.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Schema for rich results -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How much does a stairlift cost in Rochester, Buffalo, or Syracuse?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Pricing varies based on the model (straight vs curved), length of the staircase, and any custom features. Most straight stairlifts start around $3,000–$5,000 installed. We provide free in-home quotes with no obligation."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can stairlifts be installed on curved stairs?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes. We specialize in custom curved stairlifts that fit the unique shape of your staircase in older Rochester, Buffalo, and Syracuse homes."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How long does installation take?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Most straight stairlifts can be installed in a few hours. Curved models typically take 1–2 days. Our technicians are clean and respectful of your home."
        }
      }
    ]
  })} />
</Layout>
